game.name: Drone Pickup Service
game.description:
You are lucky enough to get your own drone delivery service. Does not sound it pretty exciting and interesting for you? Join Drone Pickup Service and get ready to pick up all the packages without crashing on your way! Not everything is going to be in your favor as the entire path is full of obstacles in this brand new adventure game. Make sure that your drone collects the right item and delivers it at a right location. You would lose game if you are crashed on your way. 

Many other people have already started drone pickup services in your city so there is no loss here in practicing on how to deliver items through drone. Your objective in this html5 flying game is to navigate the drone into multiple challenging conditions. Try to pick up the packages and return them to base as fast as you can to complete each level with the maximum number of stars! Feel free to fly around wind mills, houses, airplanes, cars, hills, and trees to pick up your package!

The best part is that your every successful attempt in the shortest possible time will reward you with some extra bonus points. There are 12 unique and highly-addictive and challenging levels to explore for kids, teenagers and grown-ups. This lovely quadcopter drone html5 game can easily impress the techy audience who grows up with many popular delivery services like Amazon, Uber and Instacart. Check out more funny and challenging adventure games for boys and have a blast with your friends, no download required!
